OL,3,C'Ben completed our family', father
OL,4,Csays about son killed by dangerous
OL,5,Cdriver
OL,7,FA grieving father has said "the very
OL,8,Finstance of what we live for has gone"
OL,9,Fafter a dangerous driver was sentenced
OL,10,Fto 13-and-a-half-years for killing two
OL,11,Fteenagers and leaving two others
OL,12,Fseriously injured.
OL,14,FDamian Corfield said car meets are a
OL,15,F"scourge of the earth" and that what
OL,16,Fhappened to his son should be a
OL,17,Fwarning to anyone thinking of taking
OL,18,Fpart in such events.
