OL,3,C'Ben completed our family', father
OL,4,Csays about son killed by dangerous
OL,5,Cdriver
OL,7,FMr Corfield's son Ben was 19 when
OL,8,FDhiya Al Maamoury, 56, lost control of
OL,9,Fhis heavily modified Nissan Skyline
OL,10,Fand crashed into him, killing him and
OL,11,Ffriend Liberty Charris, 16, and
OL,12,Finjuring Ethan Kilburn and Ebonie
OL,13,FParkes on November 20, 2022.
OL,15,FTwo others were also seriously injured
OL,16,Fin the collision, with Ethan Kilburn
OL,17,Fsuffering a fractured pelvis, foot and
OL,18,Fright arm while Ebonie Parkes was left
OL,19,Fwith fractured ribs, hips, leg and
OL,20,Fshoulder and a collapsed lung.
