OL,3,C'Ben completed our family', father
OL,4,Csays about son killed by dangerous
OL,5,Cdriver
OL,7,FAfter Al Maamoury was jailed at
OL,8,FWolverhampton Crown Court on Friday,
OL,9,Fspeaking beside wife Lynette, and with
OL,10,Fa pin badge of his son's face attached
OL,11,Fto his suit lapel, he said: "We've all
OL,12,Fseen these type of car meets
OL,13,Fadvertised out there."
OL,15,FHe adds: "They are a danger to all
OL,16,Froad users and they seem to have
OL,17,Fprogressed over the last 12 or 18
OL,18,Fmonths."
