OL,3,C'Ben completed our family', father
OL,4,Csays about son killed by dangerous
OL,5,Cdriver
OL,7,F"The incident that took Ben's life at
OL,8,FOldbury, there is an injunction there
OL,9,Fnow and West Midlands Police are
OL,10,Fcertainly making a strong stance on
OL,11,Fthat to stamp this practice out."
OL,13,FWhile Mr Corfield said the sentencing
OL,14,F"hasn't delivered a conclusion for us
OL,15,Fas a family", he said he believed the
OL,16,Fjudge had set a precedent with his
OL,17,Fsentence.
