OL,3,C'Ben completed our family', father
OL,4,Csays about son killed by dangerous
OL,5,Cdriver
OL,7,FHe said: "Ben's gone, we've lost our
OL,8,Fson, the light of our lives. Nothing
OL,9,Fwill take that pain away, and it's the
OL,10,Fmost excruciating, heart-wrenching
OL,11,Fpain, every second of the day.
OL,13,F"(The sentence) was far more than what
OL,14,Fus four families were expecting, and
OL,15,Fthis has got to be a warning to
OL,16,Fanybody that's involved in this type
OL,17,Fof action, that it won't be tolerated.
