OL,3,C'Ben completed our family', father
OL,4,Csays about son killed by dangerous
OL,5,Cdriver
OL,7,F"This guy showed no remorse so we are
OL,8,Fcertainly happy with the sentence
OL,9,Ftoday, but even if it was life, it
OL,10,Fcouldn't make us feel any better, but
OL,11,Fwe do appreciate the sentence today
OL,12,Fand everybody that has been involved
OL,13,Fin it."
OL,15,FSpeaking of his son, Mr Corfield said
OL,16,Fhe was a "miracle" who completed their
OL,17,Ffamily.
