OL,5,Cdriver
OL,7,F"These young people that were just
OL,8,Fstarting their lives have now lost
OL,9,Fthem because one person decided to
OL,10,Fshow off.
OL,12,F"The decisions you make when driving
OL,13,Fcan change the lives of someone
OL,14,Fforever and it takes just one second
OL,15,Fto make the wrong one."
